bard<br />\n<br />\n唔駛visa就可以入境, 並且可以無限期居留！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Norway-Svalbard.svg/800px-Norway-Svalbard.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc3%2FNorway-Svalbard.svg%2F800px-Norway-Svalbard.svg.png&h=ec0b4c60&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nD嘢好貴架。"},{"pid":"b149f3bc820cb52b4ac5a835f89a063499afc09c","tid":251850,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NNXzt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNNXzt.jpg&h=0e2d9ff4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去Svalbard<br />\n<br />\n唔駛visa就可以入境, 並且可以無限期居留！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Norway-Svalbard.svg/800px-Norway-Svalbard.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc3%2FNorway-Svalbard.svg%2F800px-Norway-Svalbard.svg.png&h=ec0b4c60&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nD嘢好貴架。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有得黎咁多要求<br />\n<br />\n地球上有地方可以不問係咪傻人都收, 仲想點"},{"pid":"b2e8a19f71c73012a9daa82ee03ac6f291cf163a","tid":251850,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NNXzt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNNXzt.jpg&h=0e2d9ff4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去Svalbard<br />\n<br />\n唔駛visa就可以入境, 並且可以無限期居留！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Norway-Svalbard.svg/800px-Norway-Svalbard.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc3%2FNorway-Svalbard.svg%2F800px-Norway-Svalbard.svg.png&h=ec0b4c60&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nD嘢好貴架。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有得黎咁多要求<br />\n<br />\n地球上有地方可以不問係咪傻人都收, 仲想點</blockquote><br />\n精神病院啱佢避世"}]}